&lt;p&gt;*Based on your experience we will pay between a Band 6 and Band 7*&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working bank is the ultimate in flexibility, without compromising your career. We are looking to recruit qualified Chemo RGNs with experience andtraining in Chemotherapy who are looking for Full time, part time orflexiblehours to work in our friendly community-minded hospital, easily accessible from London and the surrounding area and working as part of a real team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our nurse&#39;s are absolutely dedicated to providing the best possible treatment to our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To join, you must:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* Currently be registered with the NMC and have a Chemo certificate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* Be eligible to work in the UK&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* Pass an enhanced DBS check&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* Have a minimum of 6 months relevant experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer great rates, access to the NHS pension, free mandatory training and the support of a professional and friendly team from the moment you register with us, to your first shift and beyond.You can also book your shifts from the comfort of your ownhome via our online bookings system!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apply with your CV now to join the StaffBank team.&lt;/p&gt;
